{"tid":2032614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急需］一個反國安法口號","createTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:28.000Z","uid":344467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f8fd713f26b635f1d17429c128bbbfecd4461b","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"007f44fb5a75b8778dc1018a3192865825220ab6","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c4193c1e2354e0f36763c629f6a2d0c7996a8086","tid":2032614,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=fe019fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"9ddc5ef017c66e1f87ffbefac937bdc6f01a0299","tid":2032614,"uid":152412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd150b1236533c2c8a8379b63d5f6c84245d2c03","tid":2032614,"uid":301476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"P牌推"},{"pid":"02b457bbec47aef282f9c35aff872c982feecf48","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"p牌推"},{"pid":"c550e7d5a22e96bd09101ec57d38cb2716a5807a","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9aa8ddeda2215abc774ed7badd8c925ccd17f67","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"無出黎嘅手足幫推thanks"},{"pid":"2c08623b3afd36e75af09143570c40ee3cdcac69","tid":2032614,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"強推國安法 香港變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2683f1093f0e5b1855ad394ddc2d2d641a5016a0","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"97d48fd1553d6bf206202cb038b555879c8a898f","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"681fed2f3eb726b98cb0e0f84390c7d3e62d4e71","tid":2032614,"uid":344467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}